From sci-fi author Philip K. Dick (Blade Runner, Minority Report, A Scanner

extra-terrestrial source he calls VALIS. He uproots his family and moves to
Los Angeles where he becomes a successful music executive with a secret
mission to overthrow the oppressive government led by US President Fremont

Hustle) and a beautiful, mysterious woman named Silvia (Alanis Morissette

shattering proportions. Although it might cost them their freedom or even
